    {
      "name": "Time Methods",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Get Current Time",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json",
                "type": "text"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"jsonrpc\": \"2.0\",\n  \"method\": \"getCurrentTime\",\n  \"params\": {},\n  \"id\": 1\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "http://localhost:3000/rpc",
              "protocol": "http",
              "host": [
                "localhost"
              ],
              "port": "3000",
              "path": [
                "rpc"
              ]
            },
            "description": "Returns the current server time in ISO 8601 format\n\n**Method Name**: getCurrentTime\n**Parameters**: None\n**Returns**: Object with timestamp in ISO 8601 format\n\n**Example Response**:\n```json\n{\n  \"jsonrpc\": \"2.0\",\n  \"result\": {\n    \"timestamp\": \"2026-01-11T10:30:45.123Z\"\n  },\n  \"id\": 1\n}\n```"
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Get Time Zone",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json",
                "type": "text"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"jsonrpc\": \"2.0\",\n  \"method\": \"getTimeZone\",\n  \"params\": {},\n  \"id\": 2\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "http://localhost:3000/rpc",
              "protocol": "http",
              "host": [
                "localhost"
              ],
              "port": "3000",
              "path": [
                "rpc"
              ]
            },
            "description": "Returns the server's timezone information\n\n**Method Name**: getTimeZone\n**Parameters**: None\n**Returns**: Object with timezone name and UTC offset\n\n**Example Response**:\n```json\n{\n  \"jsonrpc\": \"2.0\",\n  \"result\": {\n    \"timezone\": \"America/New_York\",\n    \"offset\": \"-05:00\"\n  },\n  \"id\": 2\n}\n```"
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Get Unix Timestamp",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json",
                "type": "text"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"jsonrpc\": \"2.0\",\n  \"method\": \"getUnixTimestamp\",\n  \"params\": {},\n  \"id\": 3\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "http://localhost:3000/rpc",
              "protocol": "http",
              "host": [
                "localhost"
              ],
              "port": "3000",
              "path": [
                "rpc"
              ]
            },
            "description": "Returns the current Unix timestamp in seconds\n\n**Method Name**: getUnixTimestamp\n**Parameters**: None\n**Returns**: Object with Unix timestamp\n\n**Example Response**:\n```json\n{\n  \"jsonrpc\": \"2.0\",\n  \"result\": {\n    \"timestamp\": 1736509845\n  },\n  \"id\": 3\n}\n```"
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Error Examples",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Invalid Method Name",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json",
                "type": "text"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"jsonrpc\": \"2.0\",\n  \"method\": \"unknownMethod\",\n  \"params\": {},\n  \"id\": 99\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "http://localhost:3000/rpc",
              "protocol": "http",
              "host": [
                "localhost"
              ],
              "port": "3000",
              "path": [
                "rpc"
              ]
            },
            "description": "This request will return a -32601 (Method not found) error\n\n**Expected Response**:\n```json\n{\n  \"jsonrpc\": \"2.0\",\n  \"error\": {\n    \"code\": -32601,\n    \"message\": \"Method not found\",\n    \"data\": \"Unknown method: unknownMethod\"\n  },\n  \"id\": 99\n}\n```"
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Missing jsonrpc Version",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json",
                "type": "text"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"method\": \"getCurrentTime\",\n  \"params\": {},\n  \"id\": 100\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "http://localhost:3000/rpc",
              "protocol": "http",
              "host": [
                "localhost"
              ],
              "port": "3000",
              "path": [
                "rpc"
              ]
            },
            "description": "This request will return a -32600 (Invalid Request) error because jsonrpc field is missing\n\n**Expected Response**:\n```json\n{\n  \"jsonrpc\": \"2.0\",\n  \"error\": {\n    \"code\": -32600,\n    \"message\": \"Invalid Request\",\n    \"data\": \"jsonrpc must be \\\"2.0\\\"\"\n  },\n  \"id\": 100\n}\n```"
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Invalid jsonrpc Version",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json",
                "type": "text"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"jsonrpc\": \"1.0\",\n  \"method\": \"getCurrentTime\",\n  \"params\": {},\n  \"id\": 101\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "http://localhost:3000/rpc",
              "protocol": "http",
              "host": [
                "localhost"
              ],
              "port": "3000",
              "path": [
                "rpc"
              ]
            },
            "description": "This request will return a -32600 (Invalid Request) error because jsonrpc is not \"2.0\"\n\n**Expected Response**:\n```json\n{\n  \"jsonrpc\": \"2.0\",\n  \"error\": {\n    \"code\": -32600,\n    \"message\": \"Invalid Request\",\n    \"data\": \"jsonrpc must be \\\"2.0\\\"\"\n  },\n  \"id\": 101\n}\n```"
          },
          "response": []
        },
