            },
            "description": "This request will return a -32600 (Invalid Request) error because method field is missing\n\n**Expected Response**:\n```json\n{\n  \"jsonrpc\": \"2.0\",\n  \"error\": {\n    \"code\": -32600,\n    \"message\": \"Invalid Request\",\n    \"data\": \"method is required\"\n  },\n  \"id\": 102\n}\n```"
